OL,3,CMore Guernsey schoolchildren using
OL,4,Cactive travel to attend school
OL,6,Fschoolchildren are increasingly using
OL,7,Factive travel - such as walking or
OL,8,Fcycling - to get to and from school,
OL,9,Faccording to a new audit.
OL,11,FEarlier this week, children were
OL,12,Fencouraged to reduce their car travel
OL,13,Fto school as part of Walk to School
OL,14,Fand Alternative Transport Week.
OL,16,FGuernsey's Improvement Commission
OL,17,Fevaluated the number of primary school
OL,18,Fchildren who had incorporated active
OL,19,Ftravel into their journeys to and from
OL,20,Fschool.
