OL,3,CMore Guernsey schoolchildren using
OL,4,Cactive travel to attend school
OL,6,FThe audit found that 61% of students
OL,7,Fused active travel options to attend
OL,8,Fschool this month.
OL,10,FIt's a 10% increase from the same
OL,11,Fperiod in 2023.
OL,13,FThe Commission believes the increase
OL,14,Fis also thanks to Hautes Capelles, St
OL,15,FMary and St Michael and La Houguette
OL,16,Fschools implementing walking bus
OL,17,Finitiatives this week.
OL,19,FWalking buses are set routes where
OL,20,Fadult escorts collect and walk groups
OL,21,Fof children to and from school.
