OL,3,CMore Guernsey schoolchildren using
OL,4,Cactive travel to attend school
OL,6,FActive Travel officer Alex Costen
OL,7,Fcommented: "Walking buses are just one
OL,8,Fexample of interventions that enable
OL,9,Fchildren to travel actively.
OL,11,F"We are working with schools to make
OL,12,Factive travel the preferable option
OL,13,Ffor all children.
OL,15,F"The trick is to build upon this
OL,16,Fincrease and make it permanent and
OL,17,Fsustainable."
